title: Ep 43: What do you Really, Really, Really Want?
description: This week I swam in my gym pool asking myself this question. And while I don't have the answer yet, I hope I'm moving in the right direction. Also, why was Grease the worst movie to show little girls? Does Socrates have the answers with "Know Thyself?" or was he just really good in Bill and Ted's Excellent Adventure?
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
